<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Rosscarrock</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The Rosscarrock Community Association, with a community centre complete with a meeting room, stage, and standard kitchen, administers Rosscarrock. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Association also operates an outdoor skating rink and hosts bingo, senior programs, and youth justice programs. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">Community meetings are held the fourth Thursday of every month. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">Westbrook Mall is located in Rosscarrock and has various shopping boutiques, a food court, and restaurants, including a Boston Pizza and Rusty Cage Bar and Grill. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">Recreation-wise, Rosscarrock is in close proximity to Glendale Meadows, Edworthy Park, Douglas Fir Trail and the Shaganappi Point Golf Club.</p>
        </div>
